## Interface: 30300
## Title: DankWoW Playerbots
## Notes: The definitive playerbot command interface for the DankWoW server.
## Author: DankWoW
## Version: 0.8.1
## SavedVariables: DankWoWPlayerbotsDB
## SavedVariablesPerCharacter: DankWoWPlayerbotsCharDB
